QuestData.Title: Battle for Azsuna
QuestData.Description: The vile demon commanding the assault must be stopped. I can get us close, but once we're there I'll rely on you and your allies to help bring down the demonic forces.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Fel Commander Xeritas in Azsuna.

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Prince Farondis to begin the final assault
